title: G.I. JOE 006 (2013) (IDW) (2 covers) (digital-Empire)
description:
G.I. Joe #6


Fred Van Lente (writer)
Jamal Igle (artist)
Jamal Igle, Steve Kurth (cover artists)


Return of the fan-favorite character the MAD MONK!

The Origin of COVER GIRL!

Courtney Krieger had it all -- fame, fortune, beauty, a whirlwind life spent jetting from one exotic locale to the next. Why did she give it all up to become the G.I. JOE team member known as COVER GIRL? Her deadliest secret will be revealed here -- as well as the connection between it and COBRA'S MAD MONK, who has returned to turn New York City into an island of terror!


Full Color, 32 pages
